room_title: Escape room "Jail Break" by Escape Countdown in Sarasota
room_description:
You and your team have been arrested for attempting to steal a national treasure. Because of the high-profile nature of the crime, it is likely you will receive a lengthy jail sentence. Deputy Warden Jackson has left the area, leaving you with an opportunity to escape. You must break out of jail, crack into the computer system to erase your arrest record, find and take the evidence â€“ all within an hour!
Warning: Strobe Lights are used within this escape room.
